\c 7
\s Icala likaAkani
\p
\v 1 Kodwa abantwana bakoIsrayeli baphambuka ngesiphambeko ngokuqalekisiweyo. Ngoba uAkani indodana kaKarmi indodana kaZabidi indodana kaZera owesizwe sakoJuda wathatha kokuqalekisiweyo; ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaselubavuthela abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 22.20.\x*.
\v 2 UJoshuwa wasethuma abantu besuka eJeriko besiya eAyi eliseduze leBeti-Aveni\x + 18.12. 1 Sam. 13.5. 14.23. Hos. 4.15. 5.8. 10.5.\x* empumalanga kweBhetheli, wakhuluma kibo esithi: Yenyukani liyehlola ilizwe. Abantu basebesenyuka bayihlola iAyi\x + Gen. 28.19.\x*.
\v 3 Basebebuyela kuJoshuwa bathi kuye: Kakungenyuki bonke abantu; kakwenyuke phose amadoda azinkulungwane ezimbili loba phose amadoda azinkulungwane ezintathu ukutshaya iAyi. Ungadinisi bonke abantu \add ngo\add*kuya khona, ngoba balutshwana.
\v 4 Kwasekusenyukela khona abavela ebantwini amadoda aphosa abe zinkulungwane ezintathu; abaleka phambi kwamadoda eAyi\x + Levi 26.17. Dute. 28.25.\x*.
\v 5 Lamadoda eAyi atshaya phose amadoda angamatshumi amathathu lesithupha, axotshana lawo phambi kwesango aze afika eShebarimi, awatshayela ekwehleni. Ngakho inhliziyo yabantu yancibilika yaba ngamanzi\x + 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 6 UJoshuwa wasedabula izigqoko zakhe, wathi mbo ngobuso emhlabathini phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* kwaze kwahlwa, yena labadala bakoIsrayeli\x + 2 Sam. 1.11.\x*, bathela uthuli emakhanda abo\x + Lilo 2.10. 1 Sam. 4.12. 2 Sam. 1.2. 13.19. 15.32. Neh. 9.1. Jobe 2.12.\x*.
\v 7 UJoshuwa wasesithi: Maye Nkosi Jehova! Ubachaphiseleni lokubachaphisa lababantu iJordani ukusinikela esandleni samaAmori ukusibhubhisa? Kungathi ngabe seneliswa sahlala ngaphetsheya kweJordani\x + Eks. 5.22. 2 Kho. 3.10.\x*!
\v 8 O Nkosi, ngizakuthini, emva kokuthi uIsrayeli esephendule intamo ezitheni zakhe?
\v 9 Ngoba amaKhanani labo bonke abakhileyo elizweni bazakuzwa, basihanqe, baliqume ibizo lethu lisuke emhlabeni\x + Hlab. 83.4.\x*. Pho, uzalenzelani ibizo lakho elikhulu\x + Eks. 32.12.\x*?
\p
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuJoshuwa: Sukuma wena, uweleni kanje ngobuso bakho?
\v 11 UIsrayeli wonile; njalo baseqile isivumelwano sami engabalaya sona\x + 7.15. Dute. 17.2.\x*, bathethe futhi kokuqalekisiweyo, njalo bebile, baqamba amanga futhi, yebo bakubekile empahleni zabo\x + 6.17,18.\x*.
\v 12 Ngalokho abantwana bakoIsrayeli babengelakuma phambi kwezitha zabo\x + Nani 14.45. Hlu. 2.14.\x*, baphendula umhlana phambi kwezitha zabo\x + 7.8.\x*, ngoba beqalekisiwe\x + 7.11.\x*. Kangisayikuba lani uba lingabhubhisi okuqalekisiweyo phakathi kwenu\x + 7.11.\x*.
\v 13 Sukuma, ngcwelisa abantu, uthi: Zingcweliseleleni ikusasa\x + 3.5.\x*; ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Kukhona okuqalekisiweyo phakathi kwakho, Israyeli\x + 7.11.\x*; ungeke ume phambi kwezitha zakho lize likhuphe okuqalekisiweyo phakathi kwenu\x + 7.11.\x*.
\v 14 Ngakho ekuseni lizasondezwa ngezizwe zenu; kuzakuthi-ke isizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ezasibamba sizasondela ngensendo, losendo iN\nd kosi\nd* ezalubamba luzasondela ngezindlu, lendlu iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayibamba izasondela ngabantu\x + Hlu. 20.9.\x*.
\v 15 Kuzakuthi-ke lowo ozabanjwa lokuqalekisiweyo uzatshiswa ngomlilo, yena lakho konke alakho\x + 1 Sam. 14.38,39.\x*, ngoba eqe isivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd*, langoba enze ubuphukuphuku koIsrayeli\x + 7.11.\x*.
\p
\v 16 UJoshuwa wasevuka ekuseni kakhulu, wenza uIsrayeli wasondela ngezizwe zakhe; lesizwe sakoJuda sabanjwa;
\v 17 wasesenza usendo lwakoJuda lusondele, wabamba usendo lwakoZera\x + Nani 26.20.\x*; wenza usendo lwakoZera lusondele ngabantu; uZabidi wasebanjwa;
\v 18 wasesenza indlu yakhe isondele ngabantu; uAkani\x + 7.1.\x*, indodana kaKarmi, indodana kaZabidi, indodana kaZera, owesizwe sakoJuda, wasebanjwa\x + 1 Sam. 14.42.\x*.
\v 19 UJoshuwa wasesithi kuAkani: Ndodana yami, ake unike iN\nd kosi\nd* udumo, uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli\x + 1Isa. 42.12; 1 Sam. 6.5; Jer. 13.16; Mal. 2.2; Joha. 9.24.\x*, uvume kuye\x + Ezra 10.11. Nani 5.6,7. 2 Lan. 30.22. Dan. 9.4. Zaga 28.13.\x*; ake ungitshele lokho okwenzileyo, ungangifihleli\x + 1 Sam. 14.43.\x*.
\v 20 UAkani wasephendula uJoshuwa wathi: Isibili mina ngonile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli. Ngokunje langokunje ngikwenzile.
\v 21 Kwathi ngibona phakathi kwempango isembatho seBhabhiloni esihle esisodwa, lamashekeli esiliva angamakhulu amabili, lolimi lwegolide olulodwa osisindo salo singamashekeli angamatshumi amahlanu, ngakuhawukela, ngakuthatha, khangela-ke, kuthukuziwe emhlabathini phakathi kwethente lami, lesiliva singaphansi kwakho\x + Gen. 10.10. 11.2. 14.1.\x*.
\p
\v 22 UJoshuwa wasethuma izithunywa, zagijima zaya ethenteni, khangela-ke, kwakufihliwe ethenteni lakhe, lesiliva singaphansi kwakho.
\v 23 Bakukhupha phakathi kwethente, bakuletha kuJoshuwa lebantwaneni bonke bakoIsrayeli, bakuthululela phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 24 UJoshuwa loIsrayeli wonke ekanye laye basebemthatha uAkani indodana kaZera, lesiliva, lesembatho, lolimi lwegolide, lamadodana akhe, lamadodakazi akhe, lenkabi zakhe, labobabhemi bakhe, lezimvu zakhe, lethente lakhe, lakho konke ayelakho, bakwenyusela esihotsheni seAkori\x + 7.26; 15.7.\x*.
\v 25 UJoshuwa wasesithi: Usihlupheleni? IN\nd kosi\nd* izakuhlupha lamuhla\x + 6.18.\x*. LoIsrayeli wonke wamkhanda ngamatshe; babatshisa ngomlilo, babakhanda ngamatshe\x + Dute. 17.5.\x*.
\v 26 Bamisa phezu kwakhe inqwaba enkulu yamatshe kuze kube lamuhla\x + 8.29. 2 Sam. 18.17. Josh. 10.27. Lilo 3.53.\x*. Ngalokho iN\nd kosi\nd* yaphenduka ekuvutheni kolaka lwayo\x + Dute. 13.17.\x*. Ngakho ibizo laleyondawo labizwa \add ngokuthi\add* yisihotsha seAkori, kuze kube lamuhla\x + 7.24. Josh. 15.7. Isa. 65.10. Hos. 2.15.\x*.